detail.description: Nestled in a boutique 5-unit building, this light-filled 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath condo offers 1,418 sq ft of comfortable coastal living. The generous living room with fireplace opens to a private patio, while the galley kitchen includes in-unit laundry for added convenience. Upstairs, both bedrooms feature en-suite baths, creating an ideal layout for privacy and functionality. Additional highlights include a powder room on the main level, secure building access, and side-by-side parking in a gated garage. With its prime Santa Monica location and timeless floor plan, this home is the perfect canvas to add your personal touch and make it your own.
